description: An 11-year-old dies in Belfast's Royal Victoria Hospital after being seriously injured on Friday.
title: Buncrana: Boy dies in hospital after being struck by a van
title_page: Buncrana: Boy dies in hospital after being struck by a van - BBC News
maintext: He was seriously injured after he was struck on Slavery Road, Tullyarvan, near Buncrana, at 17:30 GMT.
